flowchart LR
    Start((Open Session)) --> Connection{Broker Connected?}
    Connection -- No --> FixConn[Prompt to update MQTT settings]
    Connection -- Yes --> Grid{All motors assigned?}
    Grid -- No --> GoGrid[Link to Grid Configurator]
    Grid -- Yes --> Patterns{Active pattern set?}
    Patterns -- No --> GoLibrary[Link to Pattern Library]
    Patterns -- Yes --> Simulation{Simulation parameters confirmed?}
    Simulation -- No --> GoSim[Link to Simulation view]
    Simulation -- Yes --> Ready((Ready to Play))
